y to the realm of \"politics\" only \ud83e\udd81 when I noticed the lack of free high-quality AI education and the worsening AI literacy gap, I didn\u2019t need anyone\u2019s PERMISSION to do something about it. I embraced my vision - free education for all so that no one is left behind - as my personal responsibility. (Kierkegaard, much?)\n\n4. Tougher AI topics like the widening class gap, widening literacy gap, culture of fear, job displacement, and lack of upskilling were only lightly touched on... the palatable answer was... \"our plan is to upskill employees so we can still fire them but they can be hired SOMEWHERE ELSE\"... lol ppl wonder why I don't care about teaching AI to big companies (answer: the gains DO NOT trickle down to you employees)\n\nNOBODY acknowledged the massive overhiring when interest rates were low, leading to multiple rounds of layoffs. NOBODY talked about how the headline \"we're firing ppl because of AI\" is often because it's a much nicer spin than ...\"we overhired when money was cheap and didn't hit revenue targets\".\n\nFull Post on Linkedin\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/posts/sabrinaramonov_time100-activity-7453076940154101760-Nfr4", "hashtags": ["TIME100"], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DXfzkfiDgoj/", "commentsCount": 194, "dimensionsHeight": 1080, "dimensionsWidth": 1080, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/671166437_17927681919272640_8116152830325120603_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFvsK4imBAY4f26580iH7IQV88fzG8A7H9G-7ACHdfqpnvKb6DpMaUPSGN8AYfpHXY&_nc_ohc=pRVNI-6dcNwQ7kNvwE-X6dt&_nc_gid=rNEOjZl-lLM53DYsGhBTGQ&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&ig_cache_key=Mzg4MjA0ODIxMTk0NzIyNzY4Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&oh=00_Af6CTFapelf3KiIOOtrpItknLoLjv0TrP6aY713Q9pwM4g&oe=6A1DF545&_nc_sid=8b3546", "images": [], "alt": null, "likesCount": 1933, "timestamp": "2026-04-24T02:03:51.000Z", "childPosts": [], "ownerUsername": "sabrina_